args: Aaaand that's one more baddie down!\nNice WORK, girl! Seriously impressive.
Really? Well, that's even better!\nAaaall righty then, let's get these guys\nall tied up like a Dragonyule goose.
Do whatever ya want—I ain't talkin'!
Haw haw! What I got to say ain't for the\nears of little Alberian girlies to hear!
Did you SERIOUSLY just call us girlies,\nyou stupid creeper?!
Fine then. If you don't wanna talk,\nI'll just, like, make you.
What kinda witchcraft ya tryin'\nto work on me, girlie?!
Oof, that is DEFINITELY your bad side.\nWell, let's see what Clix can do...
We'll make the eyes suuuper biiig...\nPut a little pink on the cheeks...
Pink on my cheeks? Oy!\nWhatcha doin' over there?!
Aw, you're gonna love it, don't worry.\nOoo, I DEF need to plump up these\neyelashes here....
Dammit, what IS this foul witchery?!
Okay, you big meanie—behold\nyour new picturesque self!
Seven hells, I am CUTE! Had no idea\nI could be that loverly, so I didn't!
I KNOW, right? You're adorbs!\nI bet you wanna run right out and\nshow this to everyone, huh?
Cor, no! How embarrassing!\nI'll never hear the end of it\nif the men see me like that!
Soooo that's a yes on my showing them?\nI was thinking I could maybe make a few\nposters, hang 'em up around tow—
...Wait, so the Imperial Army attacked\nthis area to gain control of the lake?
Aye, and that's the Goddess's truth.\nWe're plannin' to build us a big fort\nright out in the middle of the thing.
Which will TOTALLY ruin the lake's natural\nbeauty, not to mention the drinking water\nfor all the nearby villages and junk...
Oh, this is NOT happening.\nNot on my watch, bub!
I'll protect the villages AND\nall of the photo-op spots!
Oh! You interested in scenic spots, Lin?
No. But what is a photo op?

It's a place where you can take a sick pic!
Here, check this one out—me and Clix
took it earlier, and it's totally just the
prettiest thing EVER.
I! KNOW! Like, I don't really get how it\n＂works＂ exactly, but Clix here can capture\nimages of pretty much anything out there.
It's great for scenery, liiike...this one!
Ha ha ha! Ohmigosh, look at my face\nin this one! I look like a such a derp.
Ha ha! Oh, for sure. I'm totally weirding\nmyself out the more I stare at it.
But I'm still gonna keep it, because it's\nthe first time you ever smiled for me!
We were just working together as a\nunited front, so... Look, leave me alone.
I'm not here to make friends.
Wait! If you're moving on, I'm coming!\nTake me with you!
Girlies? Think maybe ya could untie\nthis poor ol' soldier before ya go?
Or leave me here if ya want,\nbut just erase that damn pictuuuure!
